statements: SELECT property_name, property_price FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE property_price < 50000;
SELECT property_name, owner_income FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE owner_income > 70000;
SELECT property_name, property_price, owner_income FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE owner_income < 100000 AND property_price > 75000;
SELECT * FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE property_id = 3;
SELECT property_name, property_price FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE property_price BETWEEN 50000 AND 80000;
SELECT property_id, property_name, property_price, owner_income FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE property_id = 1 ORDER BY property_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE owner_income > 50000 ORDER BY property_id;
SELECT property_id, property_name FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE owner_income < 40000 AND property_price > 100000 ORDER BY property_id, property_price;
SELECT property_id, property_price FROM PropertyAffordability WHERE owner_income BETWEEN 30000 AND 60000 ORDER BY property_price ASC, property_id DESC;
SELECT COUNT(property_id) AS property_count, AVG(owner_income) AS avg_income FROM PropertyAffordability;
SELECT property_id, price, property_type, location FROM property_price;
SELECT location, property_type, price, property_id FROM property_price;
SELECT price, property_type FROM property_price WHERE property_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM property_price WHERE property_type = 'Apartment' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT location, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM property_price GROUP BY location;
SELECT * FROM property_price ORDER BY price DESC, property_type ASC
SELECT property_id, price, property_type FROM property_price WHERE location = 'New York'
SELECT property_id, price, property_type FROM property_price WHERE property_type = 'Apartment' AND price > 100000 ORDER BY price ASC
SELECT income, occupation FROM income_level WHERE location = 'California' AND income > 50000 ORDER BY income DESC
SELECT * FROM property_price JOIN income_level ON property_price.location = income_level.location
SELECT * FROM property_prices;
SELECT property_name, property_price, property_location FROM property_prices;
SELECT property_id, property_name, property_type FROM property_prices ORDER BY property_id DESC;
SELECT property_location, property_price FROM property_prices WHERE property_type = 'Apartment';
SELECT property_id, property_name, property_price FROM property_prices WHERE property_price > 500000 ORDER BY property_price ASC;
SELECT * FROM property_prices ORDER BY property_id DESC;
SELECT property_name, property_price, property_location FROM property_prices WHERE property_type='Apartment';
SELECT analysis_id, property_id, income_id, affordability_score FROM affordability_analysis WHERE affordability_score > 75 ORDER BY affordability_score DESC;
SELECT AVG(property_price) AS avg_price, property_location FROM property_prices GROUP BY property_location;
SELECT * FROM income_levels WHERE income_range LIKE '%-100K%' ORDER BY income_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM property_details;
SELECT property_name, property_price FROM property_details;
SELECT property_id, property_type, property_area FROM property_details WHERE property_price > 100000;
SELECT * FROM property_owner JOIN property_details ON property_owner.property_id = property_details.property_id;
SELECT owner_name, owner_contact FROM property_owner WHERE owner_name LIKE '%John%';
SELECT * FROM property_details ORDER BY property_name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT property_name, property_price FROM property_details WHERE property_price > 50000 ORDER BY property_price ASC;

SELECT pd.property_name, ia.affordability_score, i.income_level FROM property_details pd JOIN affordability_analysis ia ON pd.property_id = ia.property_id JOIN income_levels i ON ia.income_id = i.income_id WHERE ia.affordability_score < 50 ORDER BY i.income_level DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS property_count FROM property_details;

SELECT po.owner_name, pd.property_name, ia.affordability_score FROM property_owner po JOIN property_details pd ON po.property_id = pd.property_id JOIN affordability_analysis ia ON pd.property_id = ia.property_id WHERE ia.affordability_score > 70;
SELECT * FROM Properties;
SELECT property_id, address FROM Properties WHERE price > 500000;
SELECT property_id, address, size_sqft FROM Properties ORDER BY size_sqft DESC;
SELECT name, age, email FROM Users WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY name ASC;
SELECT sale_id, sale_date, sale_price FROM PropertySales WHERE sale_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT * FROM Properties WHERE price > 500000 ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT Users.name, Users.email, Income.income FROM Users JOIN Income ON Users.user_id = Income.user_id WHERE Income.income > 60000;

SELECT Users.name, Properties.address, PropertySales.sale_price FROM Users JOIN PropertySales ON Users.user_id = PropertySales.buyer_id JOIN Properties ON PropertySales.property_id = Properties.property_id;

SELECT Users.name, Users.occupation, AffordabilityAnalysis.affordability_score FROM Users JOIN AffordabilityAnalysis ON Users.user_id = AffordabilityAnalysis.user_id WHERE AffordabilityAnalysis.affordability_score < 0.6;

SELECT Users.name, Users.age, Income.income, AffordabilityAnalysis.affordability_score FROM Users JOIN Income ON Users.user_id = Income.user_id JOIN AffordabilityAnalysis ON Users.user_id = AffordabilityAnalysis.user_id WHERE Income.income > 80000 AND AffordabilityAnalysis.affordability_score < 0.5 ORDER BY Income.income DESC LIMIT 2;
